{"tid":2266042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太子站悼8.31 區議員被捕","createTime":"2020-11-01T03:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T07:32:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64e4843f98ad20b203d77dcbe8aa9e77e9d6ddb1","tid":2266042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/E6A6B273UBBYTNA4OOESCKRZV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FE6A6B273UBBYTNA4OOESCKRZV4%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=3f53e61f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FE6A6B273UBBYTNA4OOESCKRZV4%2F&h=5a58d2ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/E6A6B273UBBYTNA4OOESCKRZV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n太子站悼8.31 區議員被捕<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵太子站8.31事件14個月，市民昨一如既往到太子站外悼念，大批警員在出口外拉起封鎖線，阻礙市民到場獻花，又截查市民及以違反限聚令來要脅在場人士離開，最終元朗區議員伍健偉及另一名男子，分別涉公眾地方行為不檢及阻礙警務人員執行職務被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7zD51hpzSFpFpi_gVuSfi2e4JNM=/616x358/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F253V3UKYVCA7AU6ATRM6AWKCY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7zD51hpzSFpFpi_gVuSfi2e4JNM%3D%2F616x358%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF253V3UKYVCA7AU6ATRM6AWKCY.gif&h=75f0c2bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■市民在太子站外悼念8.31，大批警員拉起封鎖線，區議員伍健偉與警員理論，最終被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30警佈防 趕走王婆婆<br />\n<br />\n昨下午，市民陸續到太子站B出口外獻花，約30警拉起封鎖線戒備，去年8月返深圳寓所時遭內地當局拘留的王婆婆王鳳瑤，攜黃傘到場，被警員要求離開。一名黑衫少年在附近免費派白花，遭五名防暴警截查。<br />\n<br />\n油尖旺區議員余德寶、林健文及李國權等人，在站外擺放紙箱收集市民鮮花，稱會運到沙嶺公墓拜祭，現場氣氛大致平靜。晚上8時許。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議員伍健偉與警員理論，稱只是一個人站在街上，最終亦因涉公眾地。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘭桂坊亦有市民趁萬聖節，身穿充滿抗爭意味的服飾悼念8.31，有人手持白花，頭戴印有港鐵徽章及太子站字樣的藍紅色面具，穿上印有8.31恐襲等照片的黑衣，有人手持台灣旗。<br />\n<br />\n其中盧先生將印有「沉冤待雪」的太子站外照片的紙箱蓋在頭上，手持以英文寫有8.31事件中警察襲擊無辜市民的紙張，警員截查時質疑他︰「着成咁唔似嚟玩Halloween喎，似嚟宣揚訊息喎。」盧最終獲放行，他強調有衣着打扮自由，警方無權干涉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kBie150HHJMGdhocVVfivbibzkY=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6O36TJPUIFAEPNORGP3PGHHETU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkBie150HHJMGdhocVVfivbibzkY%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6O36TJPUIFAEPNORGP3PGHHETU.jpg&h=5268e092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王婆婆王鳳瑤攜黃傘到場，被警員要求離開。"},{"pid":"cc3b89416cb3f7101d93fd0c2a3798742c845d52","tid":2266042,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"手殘負皮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51eef979a4db50ba79b7b0be08ca281d09caa5f0","tid":2266042,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cc3b89416cb3f7101d93fd0c2a3798742c845d52","tid":2266042,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"手殘負皮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"我都手殘負皮左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a27d8784cdbd4c606b52990ac517b90f6edd9db","tid":2266042,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51eef979a4db50ba79b7b0be08ca281d09caa5f0","tid":2266042,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cc3b89416cb3f7101d93fd0c2a3798742c845d52","tid":2266042,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"手殘負皮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i